  "body": "Bid validation is slow and resource-expensive.\r\n\r\nPossible improvements:\r\n1. Not validating any submissions with value below the highest non-cancellable bid\r\n2. Smarter builder reputation system (i.e. simple scoring based on time vs submission quality)\r\n3. Removing cancellations altogether (see also https://ethresear.ch/t/bid-cancellations-considered-harmful/15500, more mid than short-term)\r\n",
